attributes.action: Ban plastic toys from fast food restaurants’ kids meals
attributes.background: I buy these meals for myself and refuse the toy. But my kids love this cheap plastic rubbish... for about a minute or five. I throw so many away, even sometimes unopened in their plastic covers. With millions binned each year let’s do our environment a favour. Ban these polluting plastic toys.
